Gas!

161
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:03,833
Gas masks on!

162
00:17:03,917 --> 00:17:06,458
That, gentlemen, was a fat pig.

163
00:17:07,125 --> 00:17:08,875
If the French could aim better,

164
00:17:08,958 --> 00:17:13,292
