of the eleventh month.

924
01:47:19,375 --> 01:47:20,667
Very good.

925
01:47:21,292 --> 01:47:22,417
The war is over.

926
01:47:36,583 --> 01:47:38,623
What are you going to do now?

927
01:47:40,417 --> 01:47:42,000
