Sole shoes together?

983
01:50:54,500 --> 01:50:55,792
Are you trying to insult me?

984
01:50:57,125 --> 01:50:58,833
I can't read my wife's letters even now.

985
01:51:00,208 --> 01:51:01,528
You're going to university, Paul.

986
01:51:02,542 --> 01:51:03,875
