1005
01:54:19,167 --> 01:54:20,292
Thief!

1006
01:54:28,875 --> 01:54:30,500
Kat! Run!

1007
01:54:31,375 --> 01:54:32,375
Run!

1008
01:54:34,250 --> 01:54:35,250
Asshole!

1009
